[Music box plays melody]

02:43.571 --> 02:46.364
- Too much?

02:46.571 --> 02:47.570
- Do you really want
my opinion?

02:47.571 --> 02:50.570
- Only if you think
it's perfect.

02:50.571 --> 02:53.571
- It's perfect!

02:58.571 --> 03:01.571
- Wow, that is just super neat.

03:02.571 --> 03:05.571
Thanks so much, Donnie!

03:07.571 --> 03:09.570
[Music box closes]
Well, got to go!

03:09.571 --> 03:11.570
Got some, uh,
training to do...

03:11.571 --> 03:12.571
[Chuckles]
Thanks again, Donnie!

03:13.114 --> 03:15.570
[Door opens, closes]

03:15.571 --> 03:18.570
- I can't even imagine how
you're feeling right now.

03:18.571 --> 03:19.570
- Devastated.

03:19.571 --> 03:21.570
- Aw, man!

03:21.571 --> 03:23.570
I was totally
gonna say "devastated"!

03:23.571 --> 03:24.570
I should've just went for it.

03:24.571 --> 03:27.570
I got to learn to trust
my instincts!

03:27.571 --> 03:30.570
I mean...
That's rough, bro.

03:30.571 --> 03:32.570
- [Groans]

03:32.571 --> 03:34.570
- Smooth move, genius.

03:34.571 --> 03:37.570
It's never gonna happen, Donnie.
We're mutants.

03:37.571 --> 03:40.571
She's a girl.
You're a giant talking turtle.

03:41.571 --> 03:42.571
The sooner you get used to it,
the better.

03:43.571 --> 03:44.570
You know what you need?
Huh?

03:44.571 --> 03:46.570
Huh, buddy?
You know what you need?

03:46.571 --> 03:47.570
- You to leave?

03:47.571 --> 03:48.571
- A little forest
ninja training!

03:49.571 --> 03:50.570
Ha!
Huh? Huh?

03:50.571 --> 03:53.570
Sounds like fun, right?
Right?

03:53.571 --> 03:56.571
- [Whimpers]

04:01.571 --> 04:04.571
- [Grunting]

04:05.571 --> 04:07.570
Aw, you guys are rustier
than the <i>Titanic's</i> butt!

04:07.571 --> 04:09.570
- No, we're--

04:09.571 --> 04:10.571
- you're not in the city
anymore.

04:11.571 --> 04:13.570
You need to get used
to this new environment--

04:13.571 --> 04:16.571
no buildings, no subways.

04:18.571 --> 04:21.570
- Lots of trees.

04:21.571 --> 04:23.570
- Ugh, tell me about it.

04:23.571 --> 04:25.570
- Well, what do you think?

04:25.571 --> 04:27.570
- Hmm...

04:27.571 --> 04:28.570
Turtle hunt.

04:28.571 --> 04:31.570
- Turtle hunt.
Both: Turtle hunt?

04:31.571 --> 04:33.570
- You gonna help out, Leo?

04:33.571 --> 04:36.570
- Yeah, I--
[Groans]

04:36.571 --> 04:37.570
Sorry.

04:37.571 --> 04:41.570
I guess
I'm still not up to it.

04:41.571 --> 04:43.570
Enjoy your little hunt, guys.

04:43.571 --> 04:44.570
- Dude!

04:44.571 --> 04:45.570
- What do you mean
by "turtle hunt"?

04:45.571 --> 04:47.570
- You guys are gonna head
into the forest.

04:47.571 --> 04:49.570
I'll give you
a five-minute head start,

04:49.571 --> 04:52.570
then I hunt you down.

04:52.571 --> 04:55.570
If you can't stay hidden
for at least an hour,

04:55.571 --> 04:56.570
you'll have to...

04:56.571 --> 04:58.570
Clean out the chicken Coop.

04:58.571 --> 05:00.570
- No way!
- Not the chicken Coop, man!

05:00.571 --> 05:02.570
- It smells like
cheese fossils!

05:02.571 --> 05:05.570
- It's got spiders so big,
they play the banjo!

05:05.571 --> 05:08.570
[Banjo music plays]

05:08.571 --> 05:10.570
- We can't clean that thing!

05:10.571 --> 05:12.570
- Then get moving.

05:12.571 --> 05:14.571
[Both yell]

05:16.697 --> 05:19.570
- How do we hide
in the woods, anyway?

05:19.571 --> 05:20.571
There's no doors!

05:21.571 --> 05:22.570
- Hmm.

05:22.571 --> 05:23.570
Ah!

05:23.571 --> 05:25.570
We could climb a tree.

05:25.571 --> 05:28.570
- That's the first place
he's gonna look.

05:28.571 --> 05:30.570
Could we burrow?

05:30.571 --> 05:31.570
Do turtles burrow in the wild?

05:31.571 --> 05:34.570
- I don't know. I've never
been in the wild before.

05:34.571 --> 05:35.570
Have you?

05:35.571 --> 05:37.570
- Does Jersey count?

05:37.571 --> 05:39.570
[Distant roaring]

05:39.571 --> 05:41.570
What the heck was that?

05:41.571 --> 05:43.570
- It's got to be Raph
messing with us!

05:43.571 --> 05:46.570
Right?
- We got to hide, now!

05:46.571 --> 05:48.571
- Aw, we are so cleaning
that Coop.

05:49.571 --> 05:51.570
Raph's gonna find us up here
in, like, five seconds.

05:51.571 --> 05:55.570
- I don't think so.
- Why not?

05:55.571 --> 05:56.571
- [Growling]

05:57.571 --> 05:58.570
- Um...

05:58.571 --> 06:00.570
Hi?

06:00.571 --> 06:01.571
[Both screaming]

06:02.571 --> 06:05.571
- [Roaring]

06:16.571 --> 06:17.570
- What is it?

06:17.571 --> 06:19.570
Some kind of monkey man?

06:19.571 --> 06:22.570
- It looks like
the mythical sasquatch...

06:22.571 --> 06:23.571
Bigfoot!

06:23.739 --> 06:26.570
[Both grunt]

06:26.571 --> 06:28.570
He's too big.

06:28.571 --> 06:30.571
Run!

06:39.571 --> 06:40.571
- [Screaming]

06:41.571 --> 06:43.570
- Come on, you're not
even trying to hide!

06:43.571 --> 06:44.571
Both:
Bigfoot!

06:45.571 --> 06:46.570
- Yeah, right.

06:46.571 --> 06:49.571
If you think you're gonna get
out of cleaning that Coop by--

06:51.571 --> 06:52.570
[all screaming]

06:52.571 --> 06:56.570
Looks like we're gonna get
some real training.

06:56.571 --> 06:58.570
- [Roaring]

06:58.571 --> 07:01.570
- Booyakasha!

07:01.571 --> 07:05.571
[Yelling]

07:17.571 --> 07:21.571
- Bigfoot got some skills.

07:26.571 --> 07:28.571
- Wah!

07:32.571 --> 07:34.570
- [Crying]

07:34.571 --> 07:36.571
- Hey, are you--

07:42.571 --> 07:43.570
- stop!

07:43.571 --> 07:45.571
Guys, he's hurt!

07:47.571 --> 07:49.570
I don't think
he wants to fight us.

07:49.571 --> 07:52.570
I think he's just scared.

07:52.571 --> 07:53.570
- Scared.

07:53.571 --> 07:54.570
- He can talk?

07:54.571 --> 07:55.571
- Look at that sagittal crest.

07:56.571 --> 07:57.570
It could be
a <i>paranthropus robustus,</i>

07:57.571 --> 08:00.570
a hominid long thought extinct!

08:00.571 --> 08:02.570
- [Muffled]
Can't breathe!

08:02.571 --> 08:03.571
- Okay, okay, easy now...

08:04.571 --> 08:04.571
Easy.

08:05.571 --> 08:08.570
I can fix your arm
if you let me.

08:08.571 --> 08:09.571
It's okay.

08:10.571 --> 08:11.570
I want to help.

08:11.571 --> 08:13.570
It's not bad,
but I'd like to take you home

08:13.571 --> 08:15.570
where we can clean it up
and bandage it.

08:15.571 --> 08:18.570
Is that okay?

08:18.571 --> 08:20.570
- Hello?

08:20.571 --> 08:22.571
Anybody?

08:24.571 --> 08:25.570
- No way!

08:25.571 --> 08:28.570
We can't bring a giant ape-man
home with us!

08:28.571 --> 08:29.570
- Of course we can.

08:29.571 --> 08:32.571
Mikey?

08:34.571 --> 08:36.570
- Injured woodland creature?

08:36.571 --> 08:37.570
Bring him home.

08:37.571 --> 08:39.570
- Two to one, Raph.
Sorry.

08:39.571 --> 08:41.570
Hi.
I'm Donnie.

08:41.571 --> 08:43.571
This is Raph,
and this is Mikey.

08:44.571 --> 08:46.570
- I.
- I?

08:46.571 --> 08:48.570
Okay, your name is I?

08:48.571 --> 08:50.570
- I...

08:50.571 --> 08:52.570
No name.

08:52.571 --> 08:55.570
- Of course you have a name.

08:55.571 --> 08:58.570
You're bigfoot!

08:58.571 --> 09:02.570
- Bigfoot!
[Laughs]

09:02.571 --> 09:04.570
Bigfoot.

09:04.571 --> 09:06.570
- Will you come with us?

09:06.571 --> 09:09.570
- [Whimpers]

09:09.571 --> 09:12.570
- It's okay.
You're gonna be safe with us.

09:12.571 --> 09:16.571
- Why would he be scared of us?

09:17.571 --> 09:18.570
- Well, mama...

09:18.571 --> 09:21.570
Been hunting this hairy freak
for years now.

09:21.571 --> 09:26.570
"And now he goes and finds
hisself some more freaks!"

09:26.571 --> 09:28.570
Settle down, mama.
Ain't no little green aliens

09:28.571 --> 09:33.571
gonna save bigfoot
from the finger.

09:35.409 --> 09:37.408
- Hello?
Anybody home?

09:37.409 --> 09:38.408
We got company!

09:38.409 --> 09:41.408
- What?
You can't let anyone in.

09:41.409 --> 09:44.408
- Why is the doorway
full of hair?

09:44.409 --> 09:46.408
- And a giant butt?

09:46.409 --> 09:49.409
Come on, it's okay.

09:51.409 --> 09:53.408
- [Gasps]
- It's bigfoot!

09:53.409 --> 09:55.408
- You brought bigfoot home?

09:55.409 --> 09:58.408
- Why everyone know
bigfoot name?

09:58.409 --> 10:01.408
- Bigfoot, this is Leo,
Casey, and April.

10:01.409 --> 10:04.408
- He's hurt!
I'll get the first-aid kit.

10:04.409 --> 10:07.408
- You can't
just bring home bigfoot!

10:07.409 --> 10:08.409
- [Chuckles awkwardly]

10:08.493 --> 10:10.408
- He needs our help...

10:10.409 --> 10:12.408
Just until his arm gets better.

10:12.409 --> 10:15.408
- Come on, let's get that wound
cleaned up.

10:15.409 --> 10:17.408
- Sure, but when I wanted
to have a dog,

10:17.409 --> 10:19.408
you guys were like like,
"no way."

10:19.409 --> 10:20.408
- You guys don't get it.

10:20.409 --> 10:22.408
Bigfoot is the missing
genetic link

10:22.409 --> 10:24.408
between humans and the ape.

10:24.409 --> 10:28.408
This discovery will change
the face of science itself.

10:28.409 --> 10:31.408
- So it's bigger
than talking turtles?

10:31.409 --> 10:34.408
- [Growls]

10:34.409 --> 10:36.408
- There you go.

10:36.409 --> 10:38.408
Try not to use it too much
for the next few days.

10:38.409 --> 10:40.408
- Mm-hmm.

10:40.409 --> 10:42.408
Bigfoot thank Donnie.

10:42.409 --> 10:44.408
- No problem.

10:44.409 --> 10:47.408
- Bad man after bigfoot.

10:47.409 --> 10:50.408
Name--the finger.

10:50.409 --> 10:52.408
- The finger?

10:52.409 --> 10:53.408
- Very bad mans.

10:53.409 --> 10:56.408
But Donnie good mans.

10:56.409 --> 10:58.408
- Aw, thanks, bigfoot.

10:58.409 --> 11:02.408
- Donnie very good mans...

11:02.409 --> 11:04.408
So good.

11:04.409 --> 11:07.409
Bigfoot...

11:11.409 --> 11:13.408
- Whoa.

11:13.409 --> 11:16.408
- Ah!
- Love Donnie!

11:16.409 --> 11:17.408
- But, but, but--

11:17.409 --> 11:19.408
- bigfoot am lady!

11:19.409 --> 11:21.408
- That...Is...Great?

11:21.409 --> 11:22.408
- That...

11:22.409 --> 11:24.408
Is great!

11:24.409 --> 11:28.409
[Laughter]

11:52.409 --> 11:55.408
- Bigfoot bring meat!

11:55.409 --> 11:56.408
- Where did you--

11:56.409 --> 11:58.408
- good meat.
[Laughs]

11:58.409 --> 11:59.408
Tender, tender.

11:59.409 --> 12:02.409
- [Screams, retches]

12:04.409 --> 12:07.408
- Bigfoot make waste.

12:07.409 --> 12:10.409
- Uh, make waste?

12:15.409 --> 12:17.408
[Foghorn blares]

12:17.409 --> 12:19.408
Aah!

12:19.409 --> 12:22.409
Bigfoot!

12:27.409 --> 12:30.408
Donnie and Mikey need
to learn to blend in out here--

12:30.409 --> 12:32.408
forest stealth.

12:32.409 --> 12:35.408
If you're gonna stay with us,
at least you can help out.

12:35.409 --> 12:37.408
So show them some stuff, okay?

12:37.409 --> 12:40.408
I have to go clean out the tub.

12:40.409 --> 12:43.409
[Breathing deeply through mask]

12:46.409 --> 12:49.409
- Please don't grab
my head again.

12:54.409 --> 12:56.408
- Blend in.

12:56.409 --> 12:58.408
- I can still see him.

12:58.409 --> 13:00.409
- Mama, looks like bigfoot
got him a couple

13:01.409 --> 13:03.408
of little green alien buddies.

13:03.409 --> 13:06.408
The finger is okay with that.

13:06.409 --> 13:08.409
[Weapon clicks]

13:10.409 --> 13:12.409
- Huh?

13:14.409 --> 13:15.408
[Gasps]

13:15.409 --> 13:16.408
[Both screaming]

13:16.409 --> 13:17.408
- What are you--

13:17.409 --> 13:20.408
- ugh, you're squishing me!

13:20.409 --> 13:21.408
- Darn it!

13:21.409 --> 13:25.408
Lost 'em,
but not for long.

13:25.409 --> 13:27.409
- Come on, Leo,
give me your best!

13:27.452 --> 13:29.408
- You'll gain no ground.

13:29.409 --> 13:32.408
- Oh, man,
bigfoot is amaze-balls

13:32.409 --> 13:35.409
with the forest-stealth stuff!

13:36.409 --> 13:37.408
- Bigfoot scared.

13:37.409 --> 13:39.409
- Aw.

13:41.409 --> 13:43.408
- Finger bad!

13:43.409 --> 13:46.408
- Right, fingers are bad.

13:46.409 --> 13:48.409
Hey, Donnie,
want to play the winner?

13:51.409 --> 13:52.408
- Evening, bigfoot.

13:52.409 --> 13:54.409
What are you making?
- Food!

13:55.409 --> 13:56.409
- Aah!
- Donnie!

13:57.409 --> 13:58.409
- Um, you realize...

13:59.409 --> 14:00.408
That meat has fur?

14:00.409 --> 14:03.409
- Mm-hmm.

14:05.409 --> 14:07.408
Hmm?
[Cat screeching]

14:07.409 --> 14:08.408
- [Screaming]

14:08.409 --> 14:09.408
- [Screeching]

14:09.409 --> 14:10.408
- [Screaming]

14:10.409 --> 14:11.409
- [Screeching]

14:12.409 --> 14:16.408
- [Screaming]
- [Screeching]

14:16.409 --> 14:19.409
[Meows weakly]

14:20.409 --> 14:24.408
- Bigfoot...Need...Help.

14:24.409 --> 14:26.408
- Sure, what bigfoot wa--

14:26.409 --> 14:29.408
I mean, what do you want?

14:29.409 --> 14:32.408
- Makeover.
Huh?

14:32.409 --> 14:35.409
- Okay, and a little
off the top here.

14:36.409 --> 14:39.409
[Humming]

14:42.409 --> 14:43.408
Well?

14:43.409 --> 14:45.408
Uh...
[Laughs]

14:45.409 --> 14:47.409
So what do you think?

14:54.409 --> 14:55.408
- Eat!

14:55.409 --> 14:56.409
- Gah!

14:57.409 --> 15:00.408
Did you...

15:00.409 --> 15:04.408
Wow--whoa.
Uh, yeah, um, uh...

15:04.409 --> 15:06.408
Thank you.

15:06.409 --> 15:09.408
Got to go, bye!

15:09.409 --> 15:12.409
- [Whimpers]

15:13.409 --> 15:15.408
- Ugh.
This is so uncomfortable.

15:15.409 --> 15:17.408
Bigfoot follows me
around everywhere

15:17.409 --> 15:19.408
like a love-struck puppy.

15:19.409 --> 15:21.409
- Now you know how April feels.

15:31.409 --> 15:33.409
- [Whimpers]

15:34.409 --> 15:37.408
[Distant laughter]

15:37.409 --> 15:38.409
- So she's wearing makeup now,

15:39.409 --> 15:42.408
and she keeps
making soup for Donnie.

15:42.409 --> 15:44.408
- Do you think she's his type?

15:44.409 --> 15:46.408
- Maybe after a shave!

15:46.409 --> 15:48.408
[Both laughing]

15:48.409 --> 15:52.408
- [Whimpering]

15:52.409 --> 15:54.408
- Bigfoot, wait!

15:54.409 --> 15:57.409
- [Crying]

16:03.409 --> 16:05.408
- What is wrong with you guys?

16:05.409 --> 16:07.409
- We didn't mean
to hurt her feelings.

16:08.409 --> 16:11.408
- Bigfoot!
Wait up!

16:11.409 --> 16:14.409
- [Crying]

16:16.409 --> 16:19.408
- Mama, your boy's got 'em
right where he wants 'em.

16:19.409 --> 16:20.409
"Iffen you play
your cards right,

16:21.409 --> 16:24.408
maybe you'll get your own
alien-hunting reality show!"

16:24.409 --> 16:30.408
Ooh, just like cousin fatback!

16:30.409 --> 16:34.244
Ohhhhh, doggie!

16:37.809 --> 16:40.809
- [Crying]

16:45.809 --> 16:47.808
[Whimpering]

16:47.809 --> 16:50.808
- How many years
the finger been chasing you?

16:50.809 --> 16:52.808
Well, guess what.

16:52.809 --> 16:54.808
Mama says the chasing's over.

16:54.809 --> 16:58.808
Bigfoot, you gonna make mama
and the finger rich!

16:58.809 --> 17:00.808
"I'm so proud of you,
the finger."

17:00.809 --> 17:04.809
Aw, shucks, mama...

17:08.809 --> 17:09.808
- What the--

17:09.809 --> 17:11.808
huh?

17:11.809 --> 17:13.808
[Thud]

17:13.809 --> 17:15.808
- Puppies...

17:15.809 --> 17:17.808
Too many puppies...

17:17.809 --> 17:18.808
Aah!

17:18.809 --> 17:20.808
- Donnie, I just had the worst
dream about--

17:20.809 --> 17:21.809
- I'm not sympathetic
right now, Mikey.

17:22.809 --> 17:23.808
The finger has been debating
whether to pickle us

17:23.809 --> 17:25.808
or stuff us.

17:25.809 --> 17:27.808
- Ooh, pickle!
Pickles taste so good!

17:27.809 --> 17:29.809
- [Sighs]

